      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Allow host-local APK media sends",
        "body": "## Summary\n- allow host-read local `.apk` attachments through the existing safe-document gate\n- preserve `.apk` as `application/vnd.android.package-archive` in MIME mapping\n- add targeted media/outbound tests and a docs note for the host-local APK case\n\n## Why\nThis is a narrow follow-up to #79658.\n\n`TXT/JSON/YAML/YML` are already covered there. `APK` is a separate real-world outbound file type that still fails on the current host-local media path, so it is split into its own small PR to keep review scope tight.\n\n## Validation\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.unit-fast.config.ts src/media/mime.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.media.config.ts src/media/web-media.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.infra.config.ts src/infra/outbound/message-action-runner.media.test.ts`\n",
